{"tid":2042582,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[港台電視31] 演藝盛薈","createTime":"2020-05-30T02:00:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T11:58:16.000Z","uid":121275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"882a0422affd0577ece2426d1a002d712d90605a","tid":2042582,"uid":121275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T02:00:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cAQnDq2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcAQnDq2.jpg&h=d704d915&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n演藝盛薈(Arts On Air) 轉播或錄播本地文化藝術表演, 藉推介及導賞文藝盛事, 以提高觀眾對表演藝術的認識及欣賞興趣。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">逢星期六晚 10:45 港台電視31<br />\n《演藝盛薈》及外購藝術節目時段</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/artsonair2015\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2Fartsonair2015&d=MUobR5x4uSQxHz8Khhk%2FvG58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=a44901b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/artsonair2015</a>"},{"pid":"6e65079a127493a943317257c332b7f685693906","tid":2042582,"uid":121275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T02:01:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">風流寡婦<br />\n30/05/2020</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;《演藝盛薈》為觀眾帶來維也納輕歌劇《風流寡婦》，由匈牙利裔輕歌劇作家法蘭茲．雷哈爾譜曲。故事講述巴爾幹半島一個小國面臨破產，為了挽留該國最富有的富孀安娜，政府說服使館秘書丹尼路向她求婚，誰知丹尼路發現原來安娜是自己的舊情人。歌劇還穿插了男爵夫人與法國貴族青年的疑似婚外情，最後在一片歡聲中落幕。《風流寡婦》不僅音樂美妙醉人，而且情節幽默、感情細膩，使觀眾感到角色有血有肉，非常有共鳴。<br />\n<br />\n非凡美樂全新演繹這部經典，並由盧景文負責執導、廖國敏擔任指揮，更邀請到多位著名演唱家來港獻技，包括嘉露蓮．禾拉、李查．特洛塞爾、美根．帕奇卡諾等，加上香港名家樂友及非凡美樂合唱團同台演出，陣容強大，不容錯過。<br />\n<br />\n編導<br />\n吳紫柔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6W1Fp7s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6W1Fp7s.jpg&h=5de49dc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vDEvNkO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvDEvNkO.jpg&h=2a88176d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qPWYWd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqPWYWd9.jpg&h=a0818477&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8dN9isw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8dN9isw.jpg&h=cb4707c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zQb6kFS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzQb6kFS.jpg&h=e26a3115&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s85KRNy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs85KRNy.jpg&h=ff87c7e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bMYgHUf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbMYgHUf.jpg&h=b9bd07fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oUJo7kW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoUJo7kW.jpg&h=89d04aed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/93evNkY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F93evNkY.jpg&h=58c7cde2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Ger47E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Ger47E.jpg&h=837210c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/artsonair2015/episode/611831\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2Fartsonair2015%2Fepisode%2F611831&d=MUobR5x4uSQxHz8Khhk%2FvG58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=c3e45cf0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/artsonair2015/episode/611831</a>"},{"pid":"62c96acbb50b9e4371c1c30a0c1e0df249a1d749","tid":2042582,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T02:03:02.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"pid":"f12bc22cf1d4dde101f94f15e8b3c8c257e61802","tid":2042582,"uid":121275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30